author: Sheena McGinley
title: Watch: BTS footage of Kendall Jenner's H&M x Balmain video ad. Lots of awks dancing
text:
We really feel for her during most of this shoot. She seems to have a perma-expression of "Uh, seriously you guys?" for most of it. It's a whole different ballgame being surrounded by a load of lithe, professional dancers. At least they all get that one dance move down pat. NAILED it.
As for the clothes themselves, they're making us will it to be party season ASAP.
